## 5. Frequently Asked Questions

**Q: Can I use this for my portfolio?**
A: Yes! Portfolio demonstrations are non-commercial use, we require to request permission first.

**Q: What if I'm a solo developer building a side project?**
A: If your side project generates revenue, you need a commercial license.
We offer startup pricing for small projects.

**Q: Can I fork and modify the code?**
A: Yes for non-commercial purposes. Commercial use of modified code still
requires a license.

**Q: What if I'm already using this commercially?**
A: Contact us immediately at jasonloeve@gmail.com. We'll work with you
on retroactive licensing with fair terms.

**Q: Can I resell this software?**
A: No. Reselling requires a separate partnership/reseller agreement.

**Q: What about open-source contributions?**
A: Contributions are welcome! By contributing, you agree to license your
contributions under the same dual-license terms.

